14724.description: Scroll that summons a Milk Cow. If you relieve the Milk Cow's fatigue, you can acquire Apiga. (Recovery is only possible through Cupid's Fatigue Recovery Potion or Cupid's Powerful Fatigue Recovery Potion.) Exchange possible. Event - Milk Cow Summon Scroll

Wild Rose Pig Candy
